  "time_ut": 1661845004,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0dbd\u0ddc\u0dbb\u0dd2-\u0dbd\u0ddc\u0dbb\u0dd2 \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0da7\u0dd3 \u0daf\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db8\u0dbb\u0dd4 \u0daf\u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Two are killed in a lorry-lorry collision",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Tissamaharama police said that a small lorry traveling on Hambantota Tissamaharama road to Weerawila Tissamaharama collided with a lorry stopped in Tissapura area on the 30th at around 5.00 am. .",
        "W., a resident of Senapura, Tissamaharama, who was traveling in the small lorry, died. S. Ranjani (58) and K.M. who resided in Gagasiripura in Tissamaharama. Asela Lakmal (33) is the two. The injured Ranjith Udayakumara, a resident of Gagasiripura, has been taken to hospital with serious injuries.",
        "The dead body has been kept at Debarawewa Base Hospital mortuary. Magistrate examination is scheduled to be held today on 30th.",
        "The lorry involved in the accident and Ridurat's small lorry were also arrested and Tissamaharama police station chief police investigation A.D. A team of officers including Mr. Kariyawasam and Police Investigation Officer Pushpakumara of the Traffic Division are conducting further investigations."
      ],
